name: Butthole Coin
description: Butthole Coin is a unique meme token designed to bring humor and fun to the cryptocurrency space. Emphasizing community engagement, it aims to create a light-hearted environment while providing users with an opportunity to participate in the growing world of digital assets. The project leverages the popularity of meme culture to attract a diverse audience, encouraging interaction and collaboration among holders. With a focus on transparency and inclusivity, Butthole Coin seeks to build a vibrant community around its playful branding and innovative features.
